{
  "stem": "27150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, in-- within the government, started the-- you see, and then Hitler was already in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Personally not, because you see, I was working in a firm that sold national products.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The firm was Omtax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And another-- it worked under two, under two names-- Omtax and Kolux.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there is--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "O-M-T-A-X Proprietary Limited, and then we-- Kolux-- K-O-L-U-X, just like [INAUDIBLE] looks, looks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was all-- you see, when I finished school, you know, that means it was very hard to get jobs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I eventually got a job as a bookkeeper, a correspondent, and messenger boy, money collector all in one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then my boss went broke, and we went to Israel, and I was without a job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother, brother recommend me to one of his competitors, who had the agency of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was just about going broke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I helped my brother with his two partners, you see, to buy him off and keep the agency of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that means in 1936, I got myself an executive position, because I was replacing the import manager and the chief accountant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and at that time, I started writing my own salary, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means nothing special.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the thing was we had, from the papers, in the [INAUDIBLE], you see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in certain streets were fights, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a district, you see, where there were wholesale-- I can't remember, [INAUDIBLE]-- wholesale fruit, you know, business.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were very strong fellows, you see, porters, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whenever there was a trouble, they were calling back, because the Bund has its own fighting group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, small trouble, you see, they beat the fellow up in the street and ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
